Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll begin negotiations with them next week, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, my grandfather on my mother's side passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Were the people in that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...Granddad and Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he had fallen out of touch with his relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. The first time I've been back\Nhere in forever, and it's for a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daikichi. You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave your bag in Granddad's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I saw a girl in the garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember her. Did Haruko's kid look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't Reina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then whose kid is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. This kitchen is so awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He went pretty peacefully for someone who lived to be 79.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, that girl is your grandfather's illegitimate child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad's kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He never told me anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And apparently, his lover took off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lover? The guy was 79, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so embarrassing and shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that makes her your little sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And my aunt, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thirty years old now! Try to be a bit more sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You went peacefully, didn't you, Granddad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How much should I give?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's entirely up to you. Give as much or as little as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely, you must expect a certain amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, however much you wish to give would be appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the custom these days is to\Nhave some Buddhist scriptures read...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a posthumous Buddhist name conferred on the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it'd cost between 400,000 and 500,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fair amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daikichi. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been keeping busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Too busy to make time for his dear mother, who longs to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't even make it back for New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dai-chan. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good girl and sit quietly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.26,Alt,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are just like your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Mum told me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my brother was lonely, since he lived on his own, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they found a Baby Book...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the name "Rin" in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But pulling something like that at the age of 79...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, putting aside whether or not he's her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to hand it to the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, can you get the cushions out of the closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trade you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Leave it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina, don't run around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're awfully good at cat's cradle, Reina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and do a four step ladder next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. Reina-chan... Pass it to me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Poo bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle. Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle watching the incense for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't sleep there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go sleep in the other room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi says he'd keep an eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on my brother, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go and sleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say your last good-byes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to your mother for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina, time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say good-bye to Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A field of flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm going to make a field of flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come and say good-bye, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put these on Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellflowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.54,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: In Japanese, bellflowers are 'Rindou'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad's favourite flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be happiest with these flowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he never going to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He'll never wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are his kid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to this "Yoshii Masako"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think tracking down someone who abandoned their child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...will really lead to much good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And my brother stubbornly refused to say a word about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she hasn't even lost her baby teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She can, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's not a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Take them all and go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like an owner of a sweet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind any long-term plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,who's going to take care of her {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. We have a shop to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were just a little less strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like she hasn't even started to speak yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, you're at home all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you take her for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,T-There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time for something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know how difficult it is to raise a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And how much I've already sacrificed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't properly take care of her, it'd be less cruel to not bother at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we supposed to be finding somebody to take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're planning to do anything yourself, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to look at things a bit more realistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we don't even know whether she really is Granddad's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to say, right? Bet you haven't even thought it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest contacting a facility that will take her off our hands immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's my aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left to go with the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the tools to make them, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's still hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll have a gentle flavour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Daikichi" sounds weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, my name is Kaga Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm going to a new nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But everybody already went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he going to pick me up soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chikyuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.54,0:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uchuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.54,0:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,U... U...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Usukuchi Shouyu. {Light flavored Soy Sauce}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Light flavored Soy Sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu... Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yubikiri genman
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "Pinky Swear."
